OL,3,COne in three employers believe AI will
OL,4,Cboost productivity, research finds
OL,6,FOne in three employers believe that
OL,7,Fartificial intelligence (AI) will
OL,8,Fincrease productivity, according to
OL,9,Fresearch.
OL,11,FA survey of more than 1,000 employers
OL,12,Ffound that around one in eight thought
OL,13,FAI would give them a competitive edge
OL,14,Fand would lead to fewer staff.
OL,16,FOne in 10 of respondents to the study
OL,17,Fby the conciliation service Acas said
OL,18,Fthere would be no benefit.
