OL,3,COne in three employers believe AI will
OL,4,Cboost productivity, research finds
OL,6,FAcas chief executive Niall Mackenzie
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our survey shows optimism
OL,8,Famongst some employers about the
OL,9,Fpotential for AI to boost their
OL,10,Fproductivity, decrease costs and
OL,11,Fincrease knowledge.
OL,13,F"Used responsibly, AI has the
OL,14,Fpotential to empower workers and
OL,15,Fsupport the delivery of different
OL,16,Fworkplace tasks.
