OL,3,COne in three employers believe AI will
OL,4,Cboost productivity, research finds
OL,6,F"Businesses should be proactive in
OL,7,Fhaving early discussions about AI with
OL,8,Fstaff, trade unions, and other worker
OL,9,Frepresentatives to understand the
OL,10,Fpotential implications and ensure its
OL,11,Fadoption is well-informed.
OL,13,F"A good clear policy will help
OL,14,Fbusinesses stay safe, transparent and
OL,15,Freassure staff that they are valued."
